DONUT 13 ULTRA LIGHT TRAVEL SET

This set consists of:
- Tecline Donut 13 Mono Red with built-in mono adapter
- DIR Harness with standard harness
- Standard 3mm Aluminium Backplate
- 2 standard weight pockets
- 2 small trim pockets
- 2 tank bands
- Transport bag

Weight of the whole set: 3,2 kg
